{"id":3006,"date":"2025-06-05T13:39:34","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:39:34","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=3006"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:20:20","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:20:20","slug":"mun-dau-trang-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/mun-dau-trang-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch tr\u1ecb hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi quan t\u00e2m khi l\u00e0n da xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n nh\u1ecf, tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ee5c nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam. V\u1eady m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n kh\u00e1c? Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd an to\u00e0n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-dau-trang-la-gi\"><\/span><b>M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng vi\u00eam, thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang th\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n d\u01b0\u1edbi hai h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n d\u01b0\u1edbi da v\u00e0 m\u1ee5n c\u00e1m. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf, ch\u1ec9 t\u1eeb 1-2mm. V\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c v\u00f9ng da ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 hai b\u00ean m\u00e1, tr\u00e1n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3732\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3732\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3732\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-1.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3732\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u d\u01b0\u1edbi b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. Kh\u00f3 nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n b\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft th\u01b0\u1eddng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ee5n khi soi da d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfu xi\u00ean v\u1edbi g\u00f3c m\u1eb7t kho\u1ea3ng 30-45 \u0111\u1ed9. Nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00f2n nh\u1ecf, m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng s\u1eefa, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i v\u00e0 k\u00e9m m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-gay-mun-dau-trang\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu do l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc. Khi tuy\u1ebfn b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u00edch t\u1ee5 tr\u00ean da, l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3733\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3733\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3733 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-2-2.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-2-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-2-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-2-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-2-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3733\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1: S\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i hormone l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, khi\u1ebfn l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng x\u1ea3y ra trong c\u00e1c giai \u0111o\u1ea1n nh\u01b0: Tu\u1ed5i d\u1eady th\u00ec, Chu k\u1ef3 kinh nguy\u1ec7t, Mang thai, Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u00e3n kinh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a thu\u1ed1c: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i thu\u1ed1c (nh\u01b0 thu\u1ed1c tr\u00e1nh thai, corticosteroid,&#8230;) c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng n\u1ed9i ti\u1ebft t\u1ed1, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Di truy\u1ec1n: N\u1ebfu trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eebng b\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1n g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cao h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, t\u1ea9y trang kh\u00f4ng k\u1ef9, ho\u1eb7c r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng b\u1ecb vi khu\u1ea9n x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng tay n\u1eb7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, m\u1ee5n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 m\u1ee7,\u00a0 g\u00e2y s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 \u0111au nh\u1ee9c.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-cach-nhan-biet-mun-dau-trang\"><\/span><b>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd th\u1eafc m\u1eafc m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u00fang v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n kh\u00e1c? D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1eadn d\u1ea1ng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3734\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3734\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3734 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-3-2.webp\" alt=\"H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-3-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-3-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-3-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-3-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3734\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u00e0u s\u1eafc: M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ee5c ho\u1eb7c h\u01a1i ng\u1ea3 v\u00e0ng, do nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n n\u1eb1m k\u00edn d\u01b0\u1edbi da, kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb oxy h\u00f3a nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf t\u1eeb 1-2 mm, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f4i khi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng li ti r\u1ea3i r\u00e1c tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n: Th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng da ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 tr\u00e1n, m\u0169i, c\u1eb1m (v\u00f9ng ch\u1eef T), c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ed5, l\u01b0ng v\u00e0 ng\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da: M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng khi\u1ebfn b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da g\u1ed3 gh\u1ec1, s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng khi nh\u00ecn d\u01b0\u1edbi \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110au v\u00e0 vi\u00eam: Lo\u1ea1i m\u1ee5n n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u0111au hay vi\u00eam, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ecb k\u00edch th\u00edch ho\u1eb7c n\u1eb7n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, ch\u00fang c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ecf v\u00e0 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f3 n\u1eb7n: Do nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2u b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi da v\u00e0 l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng k\u00edn, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u0103n kho\u0103n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n kh\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn da t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"huong-dan-cach-cham-soc-da-mun-dau-trang-tu-chuyen-gia\"><\/span><strong>H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3735\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3735\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3735 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-4-2.webp\" alt=\"Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng chu\u1ea9n\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-4-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-4-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-4-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-4-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3735\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng chu\u1ea9n<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-cac-san-pham-boi-ngoai-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m b\u00f4i ngo\u00e0i da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? \u0110\u1ec3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham kh\u1ea3o c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ee9a c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Axit salicylic: Gi\u00fap t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Sulfur: Gi\u1ea3m vi khu\u1ea9n g\u00e2y m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tinh d\u1ea7u tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0: V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng kh\u00e1ng khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng vi\u00eam, tinh d\u1ea7u tr\u00e0 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu c\u00e1c n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Axit azelaic: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinoids, Adapalen, Bakuchiol&#8230;: Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ecb m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lay-nhan-mun-y-khoa\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n y khoa<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn l\u00e0 l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n y khoa t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c c\u01a1 s\u1edf da li\u1ec5u uy t\u00edn. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 v\u00f4 tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n, gi\u00fap ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 v\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"peel-da-sinh-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Peel da sinh h\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Peel da s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng acid h\u1eefu c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y da t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n l\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p n\u00e0y gi\u00fap gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da. Tuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n th\u0103m kh\u00e1m b\u00e1c s\u0129 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 peel ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, tr\u00e1nh t\u1ef1 \u00fd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"-q-a-cau-hoi-thuong-gap-lien-quan-den-mun-dau-trang-la-gi\"><\/span><b>[ Q&amp;A ] C\u00e2u h\u1ecfi th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"mun-dau-trang-co-tu-het-khong\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 h\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y l\u00e0n da xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed1t m\u1ee5n li ti, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng \u0111\u1ee5c. V\u1eady m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 h\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng? Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edd d\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, da c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u1edfi c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba hay b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebfn m\u1ea5t m\u00e0 c\u00f2n d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam, m\u1ee5n b\u1ecdc, khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c x\u1eed l\u00fd tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3736\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3736\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3736\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-5-2.webp\" alt=\"M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 h\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-5-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-5-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-5-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/28-5-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3736\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 t\u1ef1 h\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-nen-nan-mun-dau-trang-khong\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng?<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u0103n kho\u0103n li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 n\u00ean n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ch\u00fang. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ef1 \u00fd n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da, g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i s\u1eb9o r\u1ed7. Vi khu\u1ea9n t\u1eeb tay v\u00e0 d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec7t tr\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5n tr\u1edf n\u00ean nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n. Thay v\u00ec n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p x\u1eed l\u00fd an to\u00e0n nh\u01b0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u1ecb ch\u1ee9a axit salicylic, benzoyl peroxide, Retinoids ho\u1eb7c tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn t\u1eeb chuy\u00ean gia da li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y nh\u00e2n m\u1ee5n \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 <\/span><b>m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch x\u1eed l\u00fd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. M\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin trong giao ti\u1ebfp. Do \u0111\u00f3, h\u00e3y ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng th\u00f3i quen ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y, gi\u1eef da s\u1ea1ch tho\u00e1ng, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p l\u1ed1i s\u1ed1ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 th\u0103m kh\u00e1m b\u00e1c s\u0129 khi c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n th\u00eam r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m sao \u0111\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd an to\u00e0n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft qua b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3731,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3006","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3006","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3006"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3006\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3984,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3006\/revisions\/3984"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3731"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3006"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3006"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3006"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}